<div id="2011_Canadian_federal_election963" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><a href="/wiki/2011_Canadian_federal_election" title="2011 Canadian federal election">2011 Canadian federal election</a></div>
</th></tr>
<tr><td class="navbox-abovebelow" colspan="2"><div>
<ul>
<li>Outgoing: <a href="/wiki/40th_Canadian_Parliament" title="40th Canadian Parliament">Conservative minority</a>
</li>
